Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:09.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:12.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:16.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:24.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:48.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:56.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:59.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:10.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:21.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:25.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:29.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:32.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:35.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow-Slow Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this good, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Silver Fox Foxy, a man\Nwho obtains whatever he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the 160 million Berries\Nalong with the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure, I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we, the Foxy Pirates,\Nare the strongest pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:28.58,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Guy Who's the Closest to Invincible?\NAnd the Most Dangerous Man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:36.60,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fox"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Porche!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hamburg!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those five all fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, what're we gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else?! We're gonna\Nclear up the humiliation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Davy Back Fight by\Ndefeating the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Porche! Hamburg!\NWe're gonna go with Operation D!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds fun over there.\NI wonder if they're still partying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go, too, Doctor?\NI can watch our ship by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm in charge of watching the ship, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also studying. I don't wanna go at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! How dare you trick me?!\NCome out, Split-Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cool down a bit, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That afro is getting you all worked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no doubt about it.\NThe afro boosts your spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, what's with the afro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we went through\Nthe trouble of saving them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he returned\Nour kindness with malice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! And he's trying to take\Nour gold, too?! That's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, that guy is too optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get serious and go on a rampage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a ship like this will be shattered\Ninto pieces in an instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the five of us do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the four of you do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, for now, we have to\Nfigure out how to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering how that Boss is,\NI bet he's up to something sneaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like we can get out from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Choppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... If you don't come out,\Nyou... will... be... punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! I hate this kind of joke the mos--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Split-Head?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, you don't know?\N--His cluelessness knows no bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, no! Where did Boss go?!\N--Why can't he see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, if he's not around, he's not around.\NI guess I'll go look somewhere else.\N--Even for Luffy, this really takes the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, take a close look at the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... Split-Head's little sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! Enough with the disguises!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! You're Split-Head! I got fooled again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even feel like making a comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, Straw Hat! Slow-Slow Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you guys get it?! No one\Ncan escape the Slow-Slow Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, that beam's a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow-Slow Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Don't come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot! It hit them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! You dodged it well,\NStraw Hat! You play dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he know what "dirty" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, be patient for 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--There's something on the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... From here on,\Nwomen aren't allowed. It's a man's path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me. In any case,\Nlet's be careful moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like an ordinary passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. Underneath this\Npassage must be a jail,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they probably got locked up there\Nfor making blunders or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can go through a place\Nlike this with no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All right!\N--It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! I can't stand being treated like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they've been locked up in\Nthis dimly lit place all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they must be vulnerable to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we use this flash ball,\Nthey won't be able to see for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use that chance to\Nmake a break for it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Close your eyes, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Now, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--N-Nami!\N--All right! I got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahh! Hey! H-Help!\N--Let me touch her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! You're saying I should go on\Nahead and not worry about you, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahhh! Hey! Hey!\N--Ah, the smooth leg of a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nooo!\N--It's been a while...\N--How soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...? Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing? I'm eating\Nrice crackers and having some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you've gotten this far.\NI'll give you credit for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, however, having Straw Hat stranded here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you reaching here\Nare all according to my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're a navigator as\Nwell as an excellent strategy advisor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we eliminate you and Straw Hat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hat Pirates are practically wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we start now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit, huh, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! We can finally beat up Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what that is,\Nbut this one is Gorilla Pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's not "pants"!\NIt's the Gorilla Puncher 13!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Straw Hat! Gorilla Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go hide, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay!\N--Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten, have you, Straw Hat...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That when your punch touches these...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll burn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the prey of Mr. Donkey Kicker 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see... I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's trying to get Boss to forgive them\Nby humoring Boss with magic tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather forecast is thunderstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderstorm Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:11:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! You thought you could break\Nthe Gorilla Puncher 13 with lightning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't get it, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can break something\Nwith rain if it can even withstand lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your punches don't work with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gorilla Punch Golden Hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire can be put out with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Spinning Top!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Please don't come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You took so long\Nthat we missed all the action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because you got lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost in a fight between pirates,\Nso I won't whine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Then... why don't you\Nlet them be your crew again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? After they tainted the pride of pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat... You're such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! For Straw Hat's sake,\Nyou go scot-free!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you guys work for me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, his charisma is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It pisses me off for some reason.\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing, Sanji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take care, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah, yeah!\N--Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came around, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper... Why am I...? Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, you jerk! How dare you\Ndesert me and go like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it wrong, Usopp. The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see... So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he outwitted my plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our enemy, but I admit, he's brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, what are we going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to find another opponent\Nto challenge to a Davy Back Fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss is cooking up a scheme again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys. Unless we defeat them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:06.87,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fox"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to keep flying this\Nugly pirate symbol forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, there's only\None place we're headed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! I see an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's an uninhabited island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready the anchor! We'll land on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, go find some foodstuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. No rats or frogs, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How self-centered you are. Once it's\Nin your stomach, it's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got fish, shellfish, fruits...\NWe got a good catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Don't stuff your mouth like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You snacked a lot earlier. I can't\Nbelieve you're still eating so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This still isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this amount of food,\Nwe're gonna run out quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, you should eat now or it'll all be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost done, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! If you're always reading,\Nyou'll become a worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call it a bookworm, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, they're all looking this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be flustered. Any way you\Nlook at it, this is an ordinary crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so obvious, it's unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They never learn, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We're gonna destroy their ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he thinks it's a real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! Let it go, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It's trying to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance! Crab-Crab Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is finally the end of Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a crab! How dare\Nyou make me get serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did you guys get eaten\Nby this crab? How pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just get a clue already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's leave those guys alone\Nand continue with our BBQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that activity made me hungrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that one isn't done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:18:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I like this way the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Boss, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! You're hungry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself one\Nof the proud Foxy Pira--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting, Mademoiselle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is today's special lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! It looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! This is scrumptious!\NPlease come to our ship, Mr. Cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! If you ask me that,\NPorche-chan, I'll have to consider it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should definitely go. I'm begging you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.84,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fox"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. This is the communications room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, it's me. Boss is knocked out,\Nso please come and get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He's alive. Well then, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:19:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Cook! Goodbye! Your food\Nwas very delicious! I was so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take care, Porche-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure you don't have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous. If I'm gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's gonna be in charge of\NNami-san and Robin-chan's meals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun! Zoro! Let's go find\Nfoodstuffs for emergency stocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper. Were you able\Nto find any medicinal herbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I've collected most of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there may be even rarer ones on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, something's\Nbeen bugging me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this weird groove\Nis that runs down this path...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, yeah, I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks as if a bicycle passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. This is an uninhabited island, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be a trace of a bicycle\Nwhen there's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're almost through the jungle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're suddenly out in a large open space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's headed to that rock.\NIs there something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darn Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be trying to have that\Nhuge mushroom all to himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like something happened. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A raccoon dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a reindeer! See? I've got antlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who's that huge guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... Why are you frozen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho-ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Don't be so bloodthirsty, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm here on orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's a nice day, I took a stroll here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders?! From what organization?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a marine. And he's one of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,known as the World Government's\Nultimate powerhouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... An Admiral at\NNavy Headquarters... Aokiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, my, you've turned\Ninto a good-looking woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:22:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Nico Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:35.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
